    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140180/extras/b3dfa7aaa535be48bbf58952c3eb5fb7.poster.avif?t=1772074757\" width=1170 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140180/extras/b3dfa7aaa535be48bbf58952c3eb5fb7.webm?t=1772074757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140180/extras/b3dfa7aaa535be48bbf58952c3eb5fb7.mp4?t=1772074757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《祭祀地宫 THYSIASTERY》</strong> 是一款地宫探险的角色扮演游戏，通过复古风格的美术描画，重现回合制与轻肉鸽相结合的魅力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将化身一众身负烙印的角色，深入广阔且神秘的地下迷宫。在探索的途中，你可以救助、联合、依靠、培养遭遇的角色，最终逃出生天。掩藏的森林、沉没的城市和其他古代秘密，将随着你不断深入探索地宫逐一呈现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140180/extras/6a69c1f6388ea9e9e20a385d6e17bbf4.avif?t=1772074757\" width=700 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>烙印已向你发出召唤。    </strong></i> <br><i><strong>迷宫再次饥渴难耐。</strong></i> <br><i><strong>抑或，这一切仅是疯狂的征兆？</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140180/extras/d2932fecff5bb2f475d6bfe8cdcf6e01.poster.avif?t=1772074757\" width=1170 height=632 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140180/extras/d2932fecff5bb2f475d6bfe8cdcf6e01.webm?t=1772074757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140180/extras/d2932fecff5bb2f475d6bfe8cdcf6e01.mp4?t=1772074757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140180/extras/6a69c1f6388ea9e9e20a385d6e17bbf4.avif?t=1772074757\" width=700 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140180/extras/8d9e7ba2ae9884c51ab76491a806c03c.poster.avif?t=1772074757\" width=1170 height=632 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140180/extras/8d9e7ba2ae9884c51ab76491a806c03c.webm?t=1772074757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140180/extras/8d9e7ba2ae9884c51ab76491a806c03c.mp4?t=1772074757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > &quot;回合制战斗，每一次选择都有一定几率让你收割敌人，或是被敌人以其人之道宰割。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > &quot;经典的肉鸽要素，如永久死亡、程序化生成的区域和随机生成的角色，为游戏提供了极高的可玩性。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 各个角色可以学习和发现大量技能，然后教授给其他角色。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 在不同的环境中摸索，调查神秘的物件和造物，与 Labyrinth 中一部分友好的原住民彼此结交。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > &quot;多种难度修正可提高或降低难度。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 精美的复古游戏美术风格，提供多种色彩主题。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140180/extras/6a69c1f6388ea9e9e20a385d6e17bbf4.avif?t=1772074757\" width=700 height=82 /></span></p>",
